    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10096659>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2–7. Terminal male tergite. 2, Gymnochthebius fossatus. 3, Ochthebius attritus. 4, Hydraena decui. 5, H. perkinsi. 6, H. guadelupensis. 7, H. franklyni. Scale = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10096659/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10096661>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8–13. Male ventrite VII and speculum gastrale. 8, Gymnochthebius fossatus. 9, Ochthebius attritus. 10, Hydraena decui. 11, H. franklyni. 12, H. guadelupensis. 13, H. perkinsi. Scale = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10096661/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10096663>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15–20. Gonocoxite and last female tergite. 15, gonocoxite of Gymnochthebius fossatus. 16, last female tergite of G. fossatus. 17, gonocoxite of Ochthebius attritus. 18, last female tergite of O. attritus. 19, gonocoxite of Hydraena decui. 20, last female tergite of H. decui. Scale = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10096663/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10096675>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41–44. Male genitalia. 41, Ochthebius attritus (lateral view). 42, O. attritus (ventral view). 43, Gymnochthebius fossatus (lateral view). 44, G. fossatus (ventral view). Scale = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10096675/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10096677>
    dc:description "FIGURES 45–55. Spermathecae. 45, G.fossatus(lateral view). 46, G. fossatus (ventral view). 47, O. attritus (ventral view). 48, H. decui (lateral view). 49, H. decui (ventral view). 50, H. franklyni (lateral view). 51, H. franklyni (ventral view). 52, H. guadelupensis (lateral view). 53, H. guadelupensis (ventral view). 54, H. perkinsi (lateral view). 55, H. perkinsi (ventral view). Scale = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10096677/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10096679>
    dc:description "FIGURES 56–58. Distribution maps for all species of Hydraenidae in eastern Cuba. 56, squares = G. fossatus, circles = O. attritus. 57, squares = H. franklyni, circles = H. guadelupensis. 58, squares = H. decui, circles = H. perkinsi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10096679/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10096683>
    dc:description "FIGURES 62–64. Habitat of Hydraenidae species. 62, habitat of H. guadelupensis. Stream, protected area “Loma del Gato”, Santiago de Cuba (Photo by J. Lastre, 27-I-2011). 63, habitat of G. fossatus and H. perkinsi. Sevilla River, La Redonda, Santiago de Cuba (Photo by A. Deler-Hernández, 20-VII-2011). 64, habitat of O. attritus. Temporary pool, Humedal San Miguel de Parada, Santiago de Cuba (Photo by F. Cala-Riquelme, 15-VI-2009)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10096683/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

